<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/20702822" target="_blank" data-id="461609" data-za-element-name="Title">
在手持设备上使用 touchstart 事件代替 click 事件是不是个好主意？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/20702822/answer/15992377">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="1526019">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="15992377"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>94</a>
</div>

<div class="zm-votebar">
