<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/41618379" target="_blank" data-id="8854785" data-za-element-name="Title">
产品经理如何在设计产品时避免给开发挖坑?
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/41618379/answer/97103278">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="34286780">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="97103278"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>93</a>
</div>

<div class="zm-votebar">
