<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">

<span class="summary-wrapper">
<span class="author-link-line">

<a class="author-link"
data-hovercard="p$t$shotgun"
target="_blank" href="/people/shotgun"
>shotgun</a><span class="icon icon-badge-best_answerer icon-badge" data-tooltip="s$b$优秀回答者"></span></span><span class="badge-summary"><a href="/people/shotgun#hilightbadge" target="_blank">黑客 (Hacker)、网络安全、信息安全话题优秀回答者</a></span>



<span title="前前前前程序猿，前前前产品狗，前前销兽，前投资人，创业中" class="bio">
…
</span>
</span>
</div>

<div class="zm-item-vote-info" data-votecount="93" data-async-voters="1">



<span class="voters text"><a href="#" class="more text"><span class="js-voteCount">93</span>&nbsp;人赞同</a></span>


