<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/33631170" target="_blank" data-id="5659024" data-za-element-name="Title">
ReactJS 真的好吗？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/33631170/answer/68363623">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="22764390">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="68363623"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>93</a>
</div>

