<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/27580342" target="_blank" data-id="3215052" data-za-element-name="Title">
Javascript 初学者如何思考才可以把脑中的东西转换成代码写出来？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/27580342/answer/37204646">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="10272528">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="37204646"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>93</a>
</div>

