<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/24188524" target="_blank" data-id="1857361" data-za-element-name="Title">
前端开发中如何在JS文件中检测用户浏览器是否打开了调试面板（F12打开开发者工具）？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/24188524/answer/117094116">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="42322145">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="117094116"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>93</a>
</div>

